    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >感谢您体验 <i>Deep Fringe</i> 演示版！在这个开发中的版本中，您将踏入未知世界，考验您的战术技巧，并一窥 <i>Deep Fringe</i> 的精彩内容。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《深狱》是一款以生物朋克废土世界为背景的黑暗硬核策略游戏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在回合制战斗中，率领具有独特能力的小队，对环境的策略性掌控是致胜关键。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3073010/extras/26d8240e4339361c6d6676c581db66b5.avif?t=1768359368\" width=600 height=64 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在游戏中探索并改造空间；修改、摧毁或替换地格元素，以利用地形高度和效果，通过战略性地部署小队来获取战术优势。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3073010/extras/b59f88d59ec3b236b5025afca17fea81.poster.avif?t=1768359368\" width=600 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3073010/extras/b59f88d59ec3b236b5025afca17fea81.webm?t=1768359368\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3073010/extras/b59f88d59ec3b236b5025afca17fea81.mp4?t=1768359368\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3073010/extras/5a30a9f0c129294227f1eee0c843c2ed.avif?t=1768359368\" width=600 height=64 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >遭遇超乎想象的恐怖敌人：散发着腐臭气息的毒瘤怪、诡异的孢子生物、密密麻麻的幼虫潮，还有被可怖生物科技扭曲改造的敌人，正蛰伏暗处，蓄势待发 。踏入这片阴森死寂的低魔废土，你将直面狰狞的怪物，以及不择手段的危险雇佣兵。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3073010/extras/97b29f37f00508e55c83bc5918c4ccda.poster.avif?t=1768359368\" width=600 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3073010/extras/97b29f37f00508e55c83bc5918c4ccda.webm?t=1768359368\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3073010/extras/97b29f37f00508e55c83bc5918c4ccda.mp4?t=1768359368\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3073010/extras/bac5f09c1294d739d063318f743d4242.avif?t=1768359368\" width=600 height=64 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >组建独具一格的角色阵容，搭配足以毁天灭地的强大火力，深度升级武器库，让每场战斗都尽在掌控。踏入战场前精心规划，添加强力道具强化实力，同时密切关注各项战斗数据，以最万全的准备迎接每一场惊心动魄的挑战。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3073010/extras/45b32359985fbfb0e2266ff854e2545f.poster.avif?t=1768359368\" width=600 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3073010/extras/45b32359985fbfb0e2266ff854e2545f.webm?t=1768359368\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3073010/extras/45b32359985fbfb0e2266ff854e2545f.mp4?t=1768359368\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3073010/extras/4b99d2e30422e3dbab50c4c941f3e92c.avif?t=1768359368\" width=600 height=64 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >遭遇那些霸占多个地格的巨型单位，它们火力全开时，攻击足以让战局天翻地覆，瞬间扭转战斗走向。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3073010/extras/19dae55e10f1ada40089b96562aa6847.poster.avif?t=1768359368\" width=600 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3073010/extras/19dae55e10f1ada40089b96562aa6847.webm?t=1768359368\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3073010/extras/19dae55e10f1ada40089b96562aa6847.mp4?t=1768359368\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3073010/extras/a400e4dede9358dc90f6e3d936ef4163.avif?t=1768359368\" width=600 height=64 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >借助内置图形编辑器，所有游戏资源均可调用，能轻松创建自定义关卡、角色与战役。通过创意工坊，与全球玩家共享创作成果，体验无边界的游戏冒险。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3073010/extras/ef1ee132f117b97a5f0503547441128a.poster.avif?t=1768359368\" width=600 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3073010/extras/ef1ee132f117b97a5f0503547441128a.webm?t=1768359368\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3073010/extras/ef1ee132f117b97a5f0503547441128a.mp4?t=1768359368\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3073010/extras/ba42d536d8ebef2d503bebf69f50af9d.avif?t=1768359368\" width=600 height=64 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >深入危机四伏的无尽之地，每一次探险，都可能揭开那场永久改变世界的末日秘密，以及敌对势力不为人知的历史。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3073010/extras/bd8e49749298f9c7bb3cd884eb5a4df5.poster.avif?t=1768359368\" width=600 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3073010/extras/bd8e49749298f9c7bb3cd884eb5a4df5.webm?t=1768359368\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3073010/extras/bd8e49749298f9c7bb3cd884eb5a4df5.mp4?t=1768359368\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3073010/extras/bbcac5725303b52e1732456c10529551.avif?t=1768359368\" width=600 height=64 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >踏入诡谲莫测的世界，与各类人物和势力不期而遇。是暗中结盟，还是蓄意挑起纷争？每一个战略抉择，都将在黑暗中为你开辟前行之路，悄然塑造独属于你的故事轨迹。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
